{"about_the_game":"Aurascope is a 2D action-adventure collectathon platformer with light puzzle and RPG elements developed by Nick Oztok. A simple demo is currently out to showcase the what the game is shaping up to be! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Trace_Moves.gif?t=1737200628\" /><br><br>Join our friends <strong>Trace and Aurora</strong> to uncover the secrets surrounding the <strong>Aurascope</strong>, a mysterious drive from beyond the stars! Use it's abilities to help collect <strong>Energy Cores</strong> scattered throughout the lands to restore power to the Islands of Starlight! Utilize the duo's arsenal of skills to collect goodies, explore, battle foes big and small, and embark on a soon to be adventure of a lifetime!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play through an hour long demo collecting Energy Cores and Star Reactors.<br></li><li> Play alongside or against your friends in head-to-head matches in the demo's battle mode!<br></li><li> Customize the game to suit your personal preferences and gameplay style. <br></li><li> Collect achievements and see your play stats within the demo! </li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Steam_Header_Gameplay.png?t=1737200628\" /><br>\u2b50 <strong>Use the Aurascope to interact with objects, attack enemies, as a jump boost, and more!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Trace_Moves_Aurascope.gif?t=1737200628\" /><br><br>\u2b50 <strong>Acquire Energy Cores to help bring power back to the Islands of Starlight!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Trace_Energy_Core.gif?t=1737200628\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Steam_Header_Duo.png?t=1737200628\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Steam_Trace.png?t=1737200628\" /><br><strong>Trace</strong> is a lean, mean, - and with his mechanical arms, perhaps literal - platforming machine. With a wide array of moves and techniques at his disposal, he can traverse nearly any location with ease! Even without the Aurascope\u2019s abilities, he is still an extremely agile and trailblazing adventurer with a big heart.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Steam_Aurora.png?t=1737200628\" /><br><strong>Aurora</strong> is an extraordinary engineer and inventor. She never shies away from adventure and may be even more of a daredevil than Trace. She is equipped with several unique inventions of her own design in addition to being able to use the Aurascope. Her smarts and determination are what get her through the toughest situations!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/extras/Running_Together_Small.png?t=1737200628\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3188440?t=1737200628","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3188440?t=1737200628","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/70e0d09a0477865fe74e576b8abe4a7953df73c1/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737200628","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188440/70e0d09a0477865fe74e576b8abe4a7953df73c1/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737200628","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Game 